   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y68.16 (mss. 5 6 40 88 400 410 (sec. m. marg.) 2005 2007 2010 2030 2040 2101 2102 2106 4000 4010 4020 4025 4040 4050 4060 4161 4162 5020, 4056):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>hazaŋhrəm</em> āb andar kunišn <em>baēšazanąm</em> āb andar zōhr kunišn baēuuarə āb andar kunišn <em>baēšazanąm</em> āb andar zōhr kunišn</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At <em>hazaŋhrəm</em>, he has to put water. At <em>baēšazanąm</em>, he has to add water to the <em>zōhr</em>. At <em>baēuuarə</em>, he has to put water. At  
            <em>baēšazanąm</em>, he has to add water to the <em>zōhr</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
